---
title: Thai Larb Style Pork Tacos with Baby Gem Lettuce and Crushed Peanuts
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Thai Larb Style Pork Tacos in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220906_R13_W42_UK_QR12333-4_KB_Main_low-bf0bc290.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/thai-larb-style-pork-tacos-62fe15e0e412bc66021ff58d-a53c39a9.pdf
